        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-2">
        <h5>Simplicity</h5>
        <p>
          CML's OIS actuators use its patented smart metal technology. A single piece of Shape Memory Alloy (SMA) wire provides force, motion and precision position control unlike Voice Coil Motors (VCM) that require bulkier magnets, copper windings and position sensors to achieve the same purpose.
        </p>
        <p>
          Therefore, smart metal OIS products are significantly smaller, simpler and more robust. The structure comprises SMA wire and only three additional, simple parts, each the thickness of a human hair, that are produced and assembled using fully automated processes. The use of automated manufacture provides high production capacity with stable yield, tight quality control and cleanliness.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-2 gemini_exploded"></div>
    </div>
